Display results table

Source: R/f_display_results_table.R
f_display_results_table.Rd

Outputs an interactive results table suitable for HTML documents and the app. Can be further formatted (e.g. conditional formatting) to preference in the app stage. This is just a demo.

Usage

f_display_results_table(coin, type = "scores")

Arguments

coin

The coin.

type

set One of `"scores"` or `"ranks"`.

Value

An interactive table using DT.
